SIMPLE: wantonly
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wantonly
<hw>Wan"ton*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>In a wanton
manner; without regularity or restraint; loosely; sportively; gayly;
playfully; recklessly; lasciviously.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Unintentionally; accidentally.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>J. Dee.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wantonness</ent>⟦br⟧
